      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i'm being careful. but my doctor is super busy and i can't get an appointment until next week. it's just a regular headache, nothing crazy. would a single dose really do that much damage if my kidney levels have been stable lately? it just seems like a lot of trouble for a little bit of pain.",
